Privacy Policy
Last updated: December 20, 2024

This privacy policy governs your use of the Intellidraft AI application (hereafter referred to as "the App"), created by Tradewyn. We are committed to protecting your privacy and ensuring a secure user experience.

1. Data Collection
We prioritize user privacy and aim to collect the minimum amount of data necessary to provide our services.

Personal Information: We do not collect personally identifiable information (PII) such as your name, address, or contacts directly through the App.

Subscription Data: When you purchase a subscription, the transaction is processed by the respective app store (Apple App Store or Google Play Store). We receive confirmation of the purchase and a unique subscriber ID to unlock premium features, but we do not have access to your credit card details or billing address.

2. Third-Party Services
While the App does not contain advertisements, it utilizes the following third-party services to manage subscriptions and improve app performance:

Payment Processors: We use Apple/Google In-App Purchases to handle subscriptions. Their use of your personal information is governed by their respective Privacy Policies.

AI Processing: As an AI-driven tool, text or data you input may be processed by third-party AI providers (such as OpenAI or Anthropic). This data is typically used only for real-time generation and is not stored by us for marketing purposes.

3. Permissions
The App may request the following permissions to function correctly:

Internet Access: Required to communicate with AI models and validate subscription status.

Notifications: Used to provide updates regarding your drafts or subscription status (only if granted by the user).

4. Data Usage
Any data processed by the App is used solely for:

Providing and maintaining the AI drafting functionality.

Managing and validating your in-app subscription.

Improving the technical performance of the application.

5. Data Sharing
We do not sell, trade, or rent your data to third parties. We only share data with third-party service providers (like payment processors) to the extent necessary to provide the App's services.

6. Security
We implement industry-standard security measures to protect your information. Since the App processes data via secure APIs and does not store personal profiles on our own servers, the risk to your personal data is significantly minimized.

7. Children’s Privacy
The App is not intended for children under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect data from children. If you believe we have inadvertently collected information from a child under 13, please contact us immediately.

8. Changes to this Privacy Policy
Tradewyn may update this privacy policy from time to time. Any changes will be reflected with a revised "Last updated" date. We recommend reviewing this policy periodically to stay informed about how we are protecting your information.

9. Contact Us
If you have any questions or concerns about this privacy policy or the practices of Intellidraft AI, please contact us at:

